description: Feff is a commander of the Marduk forces and reports to Lord Emperor Ingues. Despite his ferocity and cruelty in combat, he does not entirely believe in the Ingues`s extreme enforcement of cultural purity and eventually turns on Ingues once he understands what http://anidb.net/ch35303 [Ishtar] is trying to do. He later confesses that he harbors feelings for http://anidb.net/ch35303 [Ishtar].Source: wiki
name: Feff
